spec_data.Name: libofx
spec_data.Description:
This is the LibOFX library.  It is a API designed to allow applications to
very easily support OFX command responses, usually provided by financial
institutions.  See http://www.ofx.net/ofx/default.asp for details and
specification.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 04 Aug 2017 12:20:51 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A library for supporting Open Financial Exchange (OFX)
